	)
	(text_box "Provide a bandpass filter to improve the PCB antenna performance.\n\nThe 5th order Butterworth filter is designed with the LTE band 20 target:\n  - Lower cutoff: 756.5 Mhz\n  - Upper cutoff: 896.5 MHz\n  - Bandwidth: 70 MHz\n  - Reference impedance: 50 Ω (both sides)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 110.49 63.5 0)
		(size 140.97 59.69)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
